text: The Bayer designation ι Normae, which is Latinized as Iota Normae and abbreviated ι Nor, is shared by two stars in the southern constellation of Norma: *ι1 Normae *ι2 Normae The pair form a double star that can be viewed with a small telescope. ==References== Normae, Iota Category:Norma (constellation)
title: Iota Normae
